  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: \r\n1) when text contains more than 3 rows and last row contains status emoji (used emoji icon in the right corner of input field) - last row is overlapped\r\n![iphonw_em](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/34385990-0e987a9e-eb2f-11e7-983c-22b38049062b.png)\r\n2) when text contains more than 3 rows and each row contains native emoji  (used emoji keyboard) - input field has additional padding (looks like empty row)\r\n![console](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/34385404-4c8675bc-eb2b-11e7-985b-3b870f61464e.png)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\ntext is visible and fits field size\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\ndepending on type of emoji, some text can be overlapped by keyboard or field can contain redundant bottom padding (see screenshots)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\nFor 1:\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to Chats\r\n- Open any chat\r\n- Type text which contains more than 3 rows and next row contains status emoj (use with emoji icon in the right corner of input field)\r\n\r\nFor 2:\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to Chats\r\n- Open any chat\r\n- Type text which contains more than 3 rows  with emoji (use from emoji keyboard)\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: \r\nIs reproducible on current develop 27/12 (0.9.11d486)\r\n\r\n* Operating System: IOS\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\n1) TF session (0:53 - 00:59): https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803590-status/builds/7375032/sessions/10/?accessToken=qQCCLX0r5SsGkrj-gGgWmrsE/sU\r\n\r\n\r\n2) TF session (0:03 - 00:52): https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803590-status/builds/7375032/sessions/11/?accessToken=Un2OIPQxgkApVutbL-vbTYW9wq0",
